\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces The training-interface shortcut and the data-level intervention. Fixed-order conversion makes position perfectly predictive of the gold verdict, so optimization can raise original-order accuracy while reducing position-swap consistency. Balanced conversion removes this global position-label correlation and forces gains to rely on information beyond a constant slot rule.}}{2}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:mechanism}{{1}{2}{The training-interface shortcut and the data-level intervention. Fixed-order conversion makes position perfectly predictive of the gold verdict, so optimization can raise original-order accuracy while reducing position-swap consistency. Balanced conversion removes this global position-label correlation and forces gains to rely on information beyond a constant slot rule}{figure.caption.1}{}}
