\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Optimization pressure amplifies the position shortcut in single-seed Qwen2.5 GRPO diagnostics. (a) As training proceeds under the accuracy reward, original-order accuracy rises while position-swap consistency falls. (b) The same tradeoff sharpens across the full-reward learning-rate sweep. The dashed marker denotes an observed transition in the tested grid, not an estimated universal threshold. Detailed checkpoint values and controls are in the~appendix.}}{5}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:optimization-pressure}{{2}{5}{Optimization pressure amplifies the position shortcut in single-seed Qwen2.5 GRPO diagnostics. (a) As training proceeds under the accuracy reward, original-order accuracy rises while position-swap consistency falls. (b) The same tradeoff sharpens across the full-reward learning-rate sweep. The dashed marker denotes an observed transition in the tested grid, not an estimated universal threshold. Detailed checkpoint values and controls are in the~appendix}{figure.caption.5}{}}
